# Normalize line endings. Without this, files committed from Windows drift to
# CRLF while others stay LF, producing whole-file "every line changed" diffs and
# unresolvable merge conflicts (the docs/*.md tangle that motivated this). Store
# and check out every text file with LF on all platforms; let git auto-detect
# which files are text. Binary assets are marked explicitly so git never touches
# them.

* text=auto eol=lf

*.png  binary
*.ico  binary
*.wav  binary
*.mp3  binary
